    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy rust on the wheel arches and rocker panels, along with several noticeable dents and fading clear coat. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears in the seating and a persistent musty odor. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission shifts harshly, making this an ideal candidate for a dedicated mechanic looking for a project or for someone in need of specific spare parts.",
